       │
       ▼
┌──────────────────┐
│ RSS Cleaner      │
│ (HTML → Text)    │
└──────┬───────────┘
       │
       ▼
┌────────────────────────┐
│ Summary Quality Check  │
│ (title ≈ summary ?)   │
└──────┬─────────────────┘
       │
       ├── GOOD → Store as-is
       │
       └── BAD → Mark for LLM backfill
                    │
                    ▼
           ┌──────────────────┐
           │ Headline-based   │
           │ LLM Summary      │
           └──────┬───────────┘
                  ▼
┌────────────────────────┐
│ ChromaDB Vector Store  │
│ (documents + metadata)│
└────────────────────────┘

STORED DOCUMENT FORMAT (in chromaDB):
------------------------------------
Stock: GOOGL
Title: ...
Summary: ...

METADATA:
-------------------------------
ticker,
timestamp
date
source_url
content_type: "news"
summary_source: Whether requires llm or not